title: Jay and Silent Bob Strike Back Soundtrack-37 tracks.mp3
description:
The Jay and Silent Bob Strike Back Soundtrack. (Complete) "37" Tracks. Unofficial.


Although there is an official movie soundtrack out there, I just thought I'd jazz it up a little. Here is MY version of the original soundtrack with a bunch of extras. I've pulled a number of sound grabs from the movie and also embedded a relevant screenshot to each track. And being somewhat of a central number to the "Smith" universe, I've limited it to 37 files.

The following tracks are in chronological order and all tags are correct. Hope you all enjoy this 15 year anniversary tribute, to what I consider to be one Smith's most mediocre/tolerable films.
